| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0235 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 9c9fac95-3240-5ba3-909e-97a0bbb8c7ea"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
